BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:resmtl-4
SEQUENCE:0
DTSTAMP:20260323T035501
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260323T173000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260323T193000
SUMMARY:Assemblée consitutive de l'OBNL "À nous la Malting!"
LOCATION:2515 Rue Delisle (métro lionel-groulx)
DESCRIPTION:2026-03-23 17:30:00\n\n2515 Rue Delisle (métro lionel-groulx)
 \n\nhttps://www.openstreetmap.org/way/347696464\n\nAprès de nombreuses an
 nées de mobilisation\, notre collectif va se constituer en OBNL (organism
 e à but non lucratif) !!!\nNous vous invitons à notre Assemblée de cons
 titution qui aura lieu :\n- Lundi le 23 mars\, à 17h30\n- Au CÉDA (2515 
 rue Delisle)\nSoyez des nôtres pour en entendre plus sur où nous en somm
 es rendu.es\, prendre des décisions pour la suite du collectif et vous im
 pliquer !\nÀ bientôt !\n...\nPendant qu'un milliardaire planifie faire 1
 00 millions $$$ avec la Malting en quelques années\, la communauté rési
 ste et s'organise pour reprendre le pouvoir et faire de la Malting un proj
 et 100% communautaire\, par et pour la communauté.\n---------------------
 ------------\nAfter many years of mobilization\, our collective is going t
 o become a nonprofit organization!\nWe invite you to our founding Assembly
 \, which will take place:\n- Monday\, March 23\, at 5:30 p.m.\n- At CÉDA 
 (2515 Delisle Street)\nJoin us to learn more about where we are now\, make
  decisions about the future of the collective\, and get involved!\nSee you
  soon!\n---------\nWhile a billionaire plans to make $100 million from Mal
 ting in a few years\, the community is resisting and organizing to take ba
 ck power and make Malting a 100% community project\, by and for the commun
 ity.\n&nbsp\;
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.openstreetmap.org/way/347696464
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:resmtl-5
SEQUENCE:0
DTSTAMP:20260323T035501
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260323T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260323T200000
SUMMARY:Spring into Action: Solidarity Crochet
LOCATION:3480 rue McTavish\, room 106 (metro Peel)
DESCRIPTION:2026-03-23 18:00:00\n\n3480 rue McTavish\, room 106 (metro Pee
 l)\n\nhttps://www.openstreetmap.org/way/30176564\n\nCome join us on March 
 23\, from 6-9 PM in the SSMU Flex Space\, in making plarn\, which is yarn 
 made from recycled plastic bags. You will learn all about the techniques o
 f making plarn with guidance. This workshop is beginner friendly!\nWithin 
 this event there will be an opportunity to share awareness about local hou
 sing projects and resources and further information for how to best suppor
 t the unhoused in our communities and beyond. Any projects completed durin
 g the workshop will be donated to Résilience Montréal.\nTea and light sn
 acks will be served.\nAccessibility:\nThe SSMU Building is wheelchair acce
 ssible.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.openstreetmap.org/way/30176564
END:VEVENT
